---
const divSoftware = '<DivSoftware>';
---

<section id='about' class='px-4 py-10 sm:px-10 md:mx-auto lg:px-40'>
	<div class='xl:max-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 sm:max-w-full'>
		<h2
			class='text-center text-2xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-left sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl'
		>
			Welcome to {divSoftware}
		</h2>
		<div
			class='flex flex-col items-center gap-12 px-5 text-sm text-white xs:text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:max-w-4xl'
		>
			<p>
				At DivSoftware, we stand at the intersection of technology and design. Our mission is to
				empower businesses with a full spectrum of technological and design solutions. Leveraging a
				diverse range of cutting-edge software technologies, we craft tailored experiences that
				resonate and engage.
			</p>
			<p>
				But our commitment goes beyond just delivering services. We prioritize excellence and
				optimization in every project, ensuring that our solutions are not only effective but also
				SEO-friendly. Dive into a world where innovation meets aesthetics with DivSoftware.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
